Task 2: Leverage Certificate Transparency Logs
Step 1: Understand Certificate Transparency
Certificate Transparency (CT) logs record all SSL/TLS certificates issued for domains. The crt.sh service provides searchable access to these logs.

Step 2: Manual crt.sh Exploration
Test manual queries:

# Query crt.sh API for subdomains
curl -s "https://crt.sh/?q=%.example.com&output=json" | head -50

# Parse JSON output
curl -s "https://crt.sh/?q=%.example.com&output=json" | python3 -m json.tool | less
