Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Google blocking automated requests

Solution: Increase delays between requests (5-10 seconds)
Use VPN or proxy rotation
Consider using Google Custom Search API
Issue: crt.sh API timeout or no results

Solution: Check internet connectivity
Verify domain has SSL certificates issued
Try manual query at https://crt.sh to confirm service availability
Issue: DNS resolution failures

Solution: Check DNS server configuration
Try alternative DNS servers (8.8.8.8, 1.1.1.1)
Verify network connectivity
Issue: HTTP connection timeouts

Solution: Increase timeout values in requests
Reduce concurrent thread count
Check firewall rules
